    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, it boasts a comprehensive service history including a documented VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation and a perfectly preserved interior, the chassis remains tight and responsive. This is a turnkey collector-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
