      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is ready for your next adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
